code: public Tuple5Builder<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4> add(T0 value0, T1 value1, T2 value2, T3 value3, T4 value4) {     tuples.add(new Tuple5<>(value0, value1, value2, value3, value4)).     return this. }
@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public Tuple5<T0, T1, T2, T3, T4>[] build() {     return tuples.toArray(new Tuple5[tuples.size()]). }
